These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: asparagus, nectarine, radish, plum, lemon, cauliflower, corn
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating plum##1
3. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating radish##1
4. the person eating lemon is between the person eating asparagus and the person eating radish##2
5. the person eating plum is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating asparagus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Food   | corn | radish | lemon | asparagus | plum | nectarine | cauliflower |

