.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
City: boston, edinburgh, colone, venice, hannover, paris, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to boston##2
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person traveling to colone is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| City   | paris | san-francisco | boston | colone | venice | edinburgh | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, sunflower, begonia, aconite, daffodil, daisy
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who growsaconite is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsmarigold##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Flower   | daisy | daffodil | aconite | marigold | zinnia | sunflower | begonia |

