.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, adventure, scientific, crime, time-travel, family
1. the person watching family movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching crime movies##2
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person watching family movies is in the middle##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | scientific | family | crime | comedy | adventure |

