.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-10::.
7 different pets are kept: dog, frog, fish, bird, rat, turtle, ferret
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the bird is the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the bird##2
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
| Pet   | turtle | dog | fish | ferret | rat | bird | frog |

